The evidence with the title 'What Obama's drilling bans mean for Alaska and the Arctic ' says Feb 5, 2015  ... President Barack Obama has effectively banned oil exploration , at least for the time being , on some 22 million acres of federal land and waters in Alaska: 12 million acres on land in the Arctic National Wildlife Refuge ( ANWR ) , and 10 million acres offshore in the Beaufort and Chukchi Seas.
